column4: "I CAN FEEL YOUR BODY  WHEN I'M LYING IN BED"
"THERE'S TOO MUCH CONFUSION GOING AROUND THROUGH MY HEAD"
"AND IT MAKES ME SO ANGRYTO KNOW THAT THE FLAME STILL BURNS"
"WHY CAN'T I GET OVER? WHEN WILL I EVER LEARN?"
"I CAN SEE YOUR FACEBUT I KNOW THAT IT'S NOT REAL"
"IT'S JUST AN ILLUSION  CAUSED BY HOW I USED TO FEEL"
"TO KNOW THAT THE FLAME WILL ALWAYS BURN"
"I KNOW NOW THAT I'LL NEVER LEARN"
